<p class="">On a point of Order, Mr. Speaker. Can you tell me why this question is taken as a Private Notice Question? What urgency is there? I understand that Private Notice Questions can be asked only as a matter of urgency.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
